{"tid":1009851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「SOD」女員工　大方分享Ｉ乳生活","createTime":"2019-02-05T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T10:22:48.000Z","uid":93998,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bd22a8a1c5c2d2df7d87d5e1dac98475a0b5f9","tid":1009851,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"「SOD」（Soft On Demand）是日本第一大AV片商，不僅捧紅過無數知名AV女優，旗下也有不少女員工轉行拍AV的例子。<br />\n<br />\n前陣子他們找來兩位宣傳部女員工和大家見面，原本說好沒有拍AV的計劃，但其中一位46歲的人妻綾瀬麻衣子，在7天後就改口宣布出道拍片。另一名23歲的日下部加奈雖然還沒鬆口答應拍AV，不過她之前曾在問答大賽中，承認自己是Ｉ罩杯，最近也在YouTube影片中，大方分享Ｉ乳生活，讓網友看了血脈賁張，無不希望她儘快出道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片中可以看到，日下部加奈儘管穿著較為寬鬆的毛衣，但胸部線條顯而易見，和一旁的同事相比，明顯大了不少。實際比較也可發現，她的胸部輕易就能放在桌子上，這可不是一般人可以做到的。此外，日下部加奈也和大家分享Ｉ乳生活的不便之處，像是下樓梯時視線容易擋住、不好買胸罩、買洋裝也很麻煩等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQyfQ6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQyfQ6a.png&h=87b20aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日下部加奈的Ｉ罩杯貨真價實，可以輕易將胸部放在桌子上。（圖／翻攝YouTube影片）<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZHDOSU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZHDOSU.png&h=21b495cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nＩ罩杯的困擾之一，就是往下看時視線會被擋住。（圖／翻攝YouTube影片）<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bXwprj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bXwprj.png&h=15620b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同事們「親手實測」（圖／翻攝YouTube影片）<br />\n為了向大家證明日下部加奈Ｉ乳的真實性，綾瀬麻衣子及編輯部同事實際觸摸，驚呼「好重」、「像西瓜一樣」，證實她的胸部如假包換，絕對沒有吹牛灌水。<br />\n<br />\n網友看完這支短片後，不斷催促日下部加奈快點出道，認為她一定會紅。其實，SOD也有不少成功說服女員工拍AV的案例，像是人氣女優市川雅美就曾是SOD宣傳部女員工，之前曾一邊在宣傳部工作，一邊兼職拍AV，現在已是日本當紅AV女優，更在2018年風光接下「惠比壽麝香葡萄」的隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190102/3151026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190102%2F3151026%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=6c686f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190102/3151026/</a>"},{"pid":"1ebcde135962e9e598dcef78426f095e91ca3630","tid":1009851,"uid":93998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"快啲下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ad980cab70ebcbeb676bd9a5e276ac0eec7c67","tid":1009851,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7e129f3f708038591ed8020060a96f1fba60f6","tid":1009851,"uid":132587,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"女員工咪又係sod宣傳技倆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95bfe887b6161d781d16d1a9efacd8c682e91e6","tid":1009851,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d7e129f3f708038591ed8020060a96f1fba60f6","tid":1009851,"uid":132587,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"女員工咪又係sod宣傳技倆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:16:02.000Z","msg":"好想佢快d下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b7578b9222cdb9d1d5a22ceaa30fbcf610b0ef","tid":1009851,"uid":4739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9d7e129f3f708038591ed8020060a96f1fba60f6","tid":1009851,"uid":132587,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"女員工咪又係sod宣傳技倆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"話明宣傳部"},{"pid":"ee956150dfbbfbe300592a406d80cdbefa32e271","tid":1009851,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike"